Name: uidbatches_max_messages
Type: INT
Default-Value: 100000
Last-Modified: 3.13.1

The maximum number of messages that the server will process in a
single UIDBATCHES command - either the number of requested batches
multiplied by the batch size, or the number of messages in the
mailbox if all batches are requested.
The default of 100000 is the minimum allowed value per the
specification. 
